topic: Book Workflow Series ("Political Magazines explorative search")

goals.1: Identify the BGP for obtaining the US magazines that write about politics
goals.2: Compare the number of social media followers and get the top five magazines along with main properties as the place of publication and subfields of work
goals.3: Compare the number of followers with the top three US magazines writing mainly about sports
goals.4: Get the name of notable employees working for The New Yorker and any other political magazine published in the US. Check if these employees have witten any book and if so get the title.
goals.5: Is any employee of The New Yorker ever been nominated for a prize or award?
